Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.40,0:20:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll surpass Itachi, soon.
Dialogue: 0,00:20:21.02,00:20:24.32,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,フンッ 言うようになったものだな。
