Dialogue: 0,00:20:30.49,00:20:34.06,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,木ノ葉警務部隊 副隊長の腕章だ。
Dialogue: 0,00:20:34.06,00:20:37.01,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,偉そうな口なら\N誰にでもきける。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.07,0:20:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk is easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.61,0:20:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Now demonstrate your skills\Nin a real mission.
Dialogue: 0,00:20:37.01,00:20:40.91,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,実際に任務について\Nお前の力を示してみろ。
Dialogue: 0,00:20:40.91,00:20:43.40,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,フンッ 望むところだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.98,0:20:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking forward to it!
